dct_title_s: Caribbean National Forest, Puerto Rico : El Yunque recreation Area, backcountry information, hiking guide / Trails Illustrated with the cooperation of National Forest Service (Recto)
dct_description_sm: "This map is based on USGS topographical maps modified and rev. by Trails Illustrated with the cooperation of the National Forest Service." Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Panel title. Includes Quad index to USGS 1:20,000 for this area, and location map. Text and descriptive indexes to points of interest and trails on verso.
